Adds Dynamic DNS (DDNS) support for the Kea DHCP server.

Manages the kea-dhcp-ddns daemon configuration including TSIG keys,
forward and reverse DNS zones, and per-subnet DDNS policy settings.

Integrates with the core Kea DHCP plugin via the plugins_run() hook
mechanism to inject DDNS parameters into kea-dhcp4.conf.

Plugin Changelog
================

1.0

Added:
* TSIG key management (HMAC-MD5 through HMAC-SHA512)
* Forward and reverse DNS zone configuration
* Per-subnet DDNS policy (send updates, qualifying suffix, conflict resolution)
* Automatic overlay injection into kea-dhcp4.conf via plugins_run() hooks
* kea-dhcp-ddns daemon configuration generation
* Log file viewer for kea-dhcp-ddns

WWW: https://github.com/brendanbank/opnsense-plugins
